{"word":"προπέμπω","slug":"προπέμπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προπέμπω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρό\">πρό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πέμπω\">πέμπω</a></el>] ‘provide travel assistance’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> escort <a href='B:510 20:38'>Ac 20:38</a>; <a href='B:510 21:5'>21:5</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> speed on one’s way,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> implication of provision made for supplies and suggestions for contacts along the way <b><a href='B:510 15:3'>Ac 15:3</a>; <a href='B:520 15:24'>Ro 15:24</a>; <a href='B:530 16:6'>1 Cor 16:6</a>, <a href='B:530 16:11'>11</a>; <a href='B:540 1:16'>2 Cor 1:16</a>; <a href='B:630 3:13'>Tit 3:13</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προπάτωρ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προπετής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}